## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the relationship between emotional states and the menstrual cycle. Individual experiences can vary widely, and more research is needed to fully understand the complex interactions involved. Additionally, cultural differences in expressing and experiencing emotions may influence the generalizability of the findings.